# ── Required ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Your API key. For Anthropic: https://console.anthropic.com/
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-xxx

# The model to use. For Anthropic, e.g. claude-sonnet-4-6 or claude-opus-4-8.
MODEL_ID=claude-sonnet-4-8


# ── Optional: Anthropic-compatible providers ─────────────────────────────────
# Many providers expose an Anthropic-compatible endpoint. To use one, point the
# SDK at it with ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL and set MODEL_ID to that provider's model.
#
# IMPORTANT: model IDs and pricing change frequently. Always confirm the CURRENT
# model id in the provider's own docs (linked below). We deliberately do NOT
# hardcode benchmark numbers here — they go stale fast and mislead.
#
#   Provider              Docs                            ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL
#   --------------------  ------------------------------  --------------------------------------
#   Anthropic (default)   https://docs.anthropic.com      (leave unset)
#   GLM / Zhipu           https://z.ai                    https://api.z.ai/api/anthropic
#   GLM / Zhipu (CN)      https://open.bigmodel.cn        https://open.bigmodel.cn/api/anthropic
#   Kimi / Moonshot       https://platform.moonshot.ai    https://api.moonshot.ai/anthropic
#   Kimi / Moonshot (CN)  https://platform.moonshot.cn    https://api.moonshot.cn/anthropic
#   DeepSeek              https://platform.deepseek.com   https://api.deepseek.com/anthropic
#   MiniMax               https://www.minimax.io          https://api.minimax.io/anthropic
#
# Example — use GLM (uncomment and set the current model id from their docs):
# ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=https://api.z.ai/api/anthropic
# MODEL_ID=<current-glm-model-id>
